metadata.name: KATIE and the CAT
metadata.description:
The BenjaminKato Club is booming! And its the talk of Katsville . Katie, a super sexy and badass crook is here with her partner in crime, Cheetara. They prey on unsuspecting BAYC holders in the dark alleys and  swipe their Nfts. You can be rest assured Katie has her eyes pinned on a  lot of loaded guests in the club and if her looks dont kill them, cheetara sure will..

My entry for the #Benjaminkato contest. Hope you guys like it.
